These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-1::.
City: venice, hannover, boston, hamburg, colone
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: dubstep, d&b, folk, blues, indie
The people have 5 different hobbies: collecting, skydiving, sudoku, hiking, reading
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: fonseca, montecristo, pall-mall, baccarat, dunhill
 1. the dunhill-smoker is on the right of the pall-mall-smoker##1
 2. the fan folk is on the left of the person traveling to hannover##1
 3. the fan indie is on the left of the fonseca-smoker##1
 4. the person traveling to boston is the person traveling to boston##1
 5. the fonseca-smoker is the fan dubstep##1
 6. the person traveling to colone is on the left of the person traveling to boston##1
 7. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 8. the person traveling to hamburg is on the right of the baccarat-smoker##1
 9. the person traveling to hamburg is on the far right##1
10. the person traveling to venice is on the left of the pall-mall-smoker##1
11. the person traveling to colone is between the person who's hobby is skydiving and the fan indie##2
12. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the fan d&b##1
13. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the person traveling to boston##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |    5     |
| City      | venice        | hannover | colone     | boston   | hamburg |
| Music-Genre   | folk     | d&b      | blues | indie   | dubstep    |
| Hobby   | hiking  | skydiving     | collecting | sudoku | reading  |
| Cigar           | montecristo | pall-mall      | dunhill     | baccarat   | fonseca     |

