.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-2::.
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: august, october, june, december, february
There are 5 different favourite beverages: 7up, iced-tea, water, milk, sprite
5 different games are played: backgammon, billiard, canasta, chess, mah-jongg
House: cottage, colonial, palace, victorian, modern
 1. the modern house is in the middle##1
 2. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the modern house##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
 5. the colonial house is between the person playing backgammon and the person drinking sprite##2
 6. the victorian house is the person who's birthday is in october##1
 7. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the cottage house##1
 8. the person playing canasta is the person drinking milk##1
 9. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
10. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
11. the person playing canasta is the person who's birthday is in june##1
12. the colonial house is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3      |    4    |     5      |
| Birthday         | december | august | february    | october  | june    |
| Beverage   | sprite    | iced-tea       | water      | 7up | milk        |
| Game   | mah-jongg   | billiard     | backgammon    | chess  | canasta     |
| House     | palace    | colonial | modern | victorian | cottage |

