.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-3::.
5 different games are played: monopoly, snooker, go, billiard, poker
The people have 5 different jobs:  dressmaker, engineer, pilot, journalist, paramedic
There are 5 different nationalities: spanish, mexican, american, indonesian, french
There 5 different types of food: strawberry, lettuce, potato, zucchini, carrot
 1. the person playing poker is the mexican##1
 2. the person eating zucchini is in the middle##1
 3. the indonesian is in the middle##1
 4. the dressmaker is in the middle##1
 5. the person playing poker is on the right of the person eating lettuce##1
 6. the person playing snooker is on the left of the spanish##1
 7. the french is on the left of the person eating potato##1
 8. the dressmaker is on the right of the engineer##1
 9. the american is on the far left##1
10. the person eating strawberry is the journalist##1
11. the person playing go is on the right of the person eating carrot##1
12. the person playing billiard is on the right of the french##1
13. the person eating carrot is between the paramedic and the person playing go##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4       |       5       |
| Game         | monopoly | poker     | go   | snooker   | billiard |
| Job   | paramedic  | engineer | dressmaker | journalist | pilot        |
| Nationality   | american      | mexican      | indonesian       | french       | spanish       |
| Food         | lettuce | carrot  | zucchini    | strawberry    | potato        |

