 2. the doctor is on the right of the person who likes fuchsia##1
 3. the dannemann-smoker is on the left of the bolivar-smoker##1
 4. the owner of the chinchilla is between the person who likes pink and the dunhill-smoker##2
 5. the dannemann-smoker is on the right of the designer##1
 6. the person who likes lavender is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
 7. the designer is on the right of the chaman-smoker##1
 8. the project-manager is the person who likes fuchsia##1
 9. the person who likes lavender is in the middle##1
10. the person who likes pink is the owner of the hedgehog##1
11. the fisherman is on the right of the designer##1
12. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the person who likes chestnut##1
13. the person who likes fuchsia is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5     |
| Cigar          | bluemaster  | chaman     | dunhill   | dannemann     | bolivar |
