.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-17::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: lavender, ebony, purple, emerald, red
5 different pets are kept: horse, rabbit, frog, pony, turtle
There 5 different types of food: peach, mango, orange, watermelon, carrot
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: november, october, may, august, january
 1. the person eating carrot is between the person who's birthday is in october and the person eating mango##2
 2. the person eating orange is on the left of the person eating watermelon##1
 3. the person who likes ebony is the owner of the pony##1
 4. the person who likes lavender is on the right of the person eating carrot##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who likes ebony##1
 6. the owner of the pony is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
 8. the owner of the frog is on the left of the person who likes ebony##1
 9. the owner of the horse is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
10. the person eating orange is on the far left##1
11. the person who's birthday is in may is between the person eating orange and the owner of the frog##2
12. the person who likes emerald is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
13. the person who likes purple is on the left of the person who likes emerald##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5      |
| Color    | purple       | emerald    | red | ebony  | lavender        |
| Pet       | turtle | horse | frog  | pony | rabbit    |
| Food       | orange        | watermelon   | mango  | carrot   | peach |
| Birthday   | august       | may      | january      | november | october  |

