.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-18::.
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: march, august, october, april, may
5 different pets are kept: mouse, hamster, dog, hedgehog, pony
House: townhouse, modern, ranch-style, tower, cottage
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, ritmeester, dannemann, montecristo, dunhill
 1. the dannemann-smoker is on the left of the modern house##1
 2. the owner of the hedgehog is between the ranch-style house and the owner of the dog##2
 3. the person who's birthday is in april is the owner of the hedgehog##1
 4. the cottage house is on the right of the montecristo-smoker##1
 5. the townhouse house is in the middle##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in april is between the owner of the pony and the ritmeester-smoker##2
 7. the montecristo-smoker is the person who's birthday is in october##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in march is the dannemann-smoker##1
 9. the old-henry-smoker is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
10. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the ranch-style house##1
11. the owner of the dog is the modern house##1
12. the tower house is on the far left##1
13. the person who's birthday is in may is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2       |     3     |    4     |     5      |
| Birthday      | march      | august         | april      | october | may     |
| Pet           | hamster | dog | hedgehog | pony    | mouse  |
