.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-19::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, juice, milk, sprite, tea
There 5 different types of food: pumpkin, cherry, onion, raspberry, cauliflower
5 different games are played: billiard, backgammon, go, snooker, canasta
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: trance, rock, country, reggae, electronic
 1. the person playing canasta is on the right of the fan rock##1
 2. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the person eating cherry##1
 3. the person drinking tea is on the left of the fan electronic##1
 4. the fan country is on the far left##1
 5. the person playing backgammon is between the person eating pumpkin and the person playing billiard##2
 6. the person eating pumpkin is on the far left##1
 7. the person drinking milk is between the fan trance and the person drinking tea##2
 8. the person drinking juice is between the person drinking sprite and the person drinking almond-milk##2
 9. the person playing snooker is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
10. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person eating cauliflower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |     4      |     5      |
| Beverage         | tea  | milk | sprite   | juice      | almond-milk |
| Food   | pumpkin   | raspberry    | cherry | cauliflower | onion      |
| Game           | go | backgammon    | billiard       | snooker     | canasta      |
| Music-Genre     | country | electronic        | trance  | rock        | reggae    |

