.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-20::.
House: tower, modern, craftsman, montecristo-climbing, colonial
There are 5 different favourite colors: fuchsia, mauve, grey, white, emerald
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, bluemaster, blend, dannemann, montecristo
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: climbing, skateboarding, rugby, baseball, swimming
 1. the tower house is on the left of the person who likes fuchsia##1
 2. the person who likes emerald is between the person who's sport is baseball and the montecristo-smoker##2
 3. the montecristo-smoker is on the right of the colonial house##1
 4. the person who likes emerald is the cain-smoker##1
 5. the cain-smoker is between the person who's sport is swimming and the blend-smoker##2
 6. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the colonial house##1
 7. the person who likes grey is the dannemann-smoker##1
 8. the montecristo-climbing house is the bluemaster-smoker##1
 9. the person who's sport is climbing is the bluemaster-smoker##1
10. the montecristo-climbing house is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1
11. the person who likes emerald is on the left of the modern house##1
12. the person who likes mauve is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3    |      4       |       5       |
| House         | craftsman    | colonial  | modern  | tower      | montecristo-climbing |
| Color   | mauve    | emerald   | white | grey | fuchsia   |
| Cigar   | blend | cain    | montecristo    | dannemann       | bluemaster         |
| Sport   | baseball  | skateboarding | swimming    | rugby     | climbing      |

 